description: If you're looking for the finest Indian food on the streets of Chicago, going anywhere else would be pure Naansense! Fast, delicious, casual Indian cuisine on the street food scene is here to take you by storm! Delicious, flavorful dishes made from the best ingredients are on this truck's menu today. For the best Rice Bowls, Roti Rolls, Naanwiches, and more, nobody beats Little Naansense!
name: Little Naansense
